!
!	THIS ROUTINE WILL CAUSE THE COPY BUFFER TO
!	HAVE THE LINE WITH THE INDICATED ADDRESS BE THE
!	FIRST IN THE BUFFER, AND CAUSE IT TO BE WRITTEN OUT
!	TO THE OUTPUT FILE WHEN THE BUFFER FILLS
!
